  "response": "To obtain mark-sheet transcripts from Jadavpur University, you typically need to follow these steps:\n\n1. Contact the University Examination Department:\n- Visit the university's official website (www.jaduniv.edu.in)\n- Find the Examination section or Contact details for the Examination Department\n\n2. Required Documents:\n- Completed application form\n- Proof of alumni status\n- Copy of marksheets/degree\n- Identity proof\n- Passport-sized photographs\n- Prescribed fees for transcript processing\n\n3. Application Process:\n- Collect/download the transcript request form\n- Fill out the form with accurate details\n- Attach all necessary documents\n- Submit the application in person or by post\n\n4. Payment:\n- Pay the prescribed fees for transcript processing\n- Fees can usually be paid through demand draft or online payment methods\n\n5. Processing Time:\n- Typically takes 2-4 weeks\n- May vary depending on current workload\n\n6. Delivery Options:\n- Collect in person\n- Send by registered post\n- Directly sent to specified institution\n\nRecommended: Contact the university's examination department directly for most updated and specific instructions.\n\nNote: Process might have slight variations, so confirming current procedures is advisable.",
